  <itemBody>
    <div class="grid-row">
      <div class="col-12">
        <h4>You have decided to only let the first 1.000 guests in. The rest are denied entrance. You get a text message from a dissatisfied costumer the next day. <br/>
<img src="forlystelsesparkopg8_2.png" alt="forlystelsesparkopg8_2" width="48%" type="image/png"/>(Hi. I should have been at the opening party in your park yesterday. When I came, I was just told that I couldn't get in. My best friend was allowed in. We were supposed to meet, but were unable to. It is not good enough! I don't think that I ever want to visit your park again. Kind regards, Henry.)</h4>
        <h6>Below are 5 different answers for Henry. The tone of them are quite different. Pick the right description of the tone, by marking the at every option with an x.</h6>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-row">
      <div class="col-12">
        <matchInteraction responseIdentifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" maxAssociations="0" minAssociations="0">
          <prompt/>
          <simpleMatchSet>
            <simpleAssociableChoice identifier="neutral" fixed="false" showHide="show" matchMax="0" matchMin="0">Neutral</simpleAssociableChoice>
            <simpleAssociableChoice identifier="rude" fixed="false" showHide="show" matchMax="0" matchMin="0">Rude</simpleAssociableChoice>
            <simpleAssociableChoice identifier="nice" fixed="false" showHide="show" matchMax="0" matchMin="0">Nice</simpleAssociableChoice>
          </simpleMatchSet>
          <simpleMatchSet>
            <simpleAssociableChoice identifier="parkfull" fixed="false" showHide="show" matchMax="1" matchMin="0">Hi. The park was filled. Therefore, you were not allowed in. Try again another day.</simpleAssociableChoice>
            <simpleAssociableChoice identifier="notallowed" fixed="false" showHide="show" matchMax="1" matchMin="0">Hi Henry. We wanted to have let you in, but were not allowed to do so by the firefighters. We apoligize!</simpleAssociableChoice>
            <simpleAssociableChoice identifier="freeticket" fixed="false" showHide="show" matchMax="1" matchMin="0">
              <div>Hi Henry. We understand that it was an annoying experience. As a way to burry the hatchet, we would like to offer you free tickets for another day.</div>
            </simpleAssociableChoice>
            <simpleAssociableChoice identifier="rules" fixed="false" showHide="show" matchMax="1" matchMin="0">
              <div>Hi Henry. It is what it is. There are rules, and it is not our fault. But it was good for your friend, that he came in.</div>
            </simpleAssociableChoice>
            <simpleAssociableChoice identifier="understanding" fixed="false" showHide="show" matchMax="1" matchMin="0">
              <div>Hi Henry. We understand that you are dissapointed. We hope that you will come back again another time.</div>
            </simpleAssociableChoice>
          </simpleMatchSet>
        </matchInteraction>
      </div>
    </div>
